THIS ISN'T FAIR."

17:08.900 --> 17:10.467 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
>> YES, IT IS NOT FAIR FOR THE

17:10.467 --> 17:13.333 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
PATIENT, I AGREE WITH YOU.

