AS A PRACTICE, OUR POLICY IS TO

17:15.333 --> 17:16.167 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
WORK WITH THE PATIENT ON OUT-OF-

17:16.167 --> 17:17.700 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
NETWORK PAYMENT.

17:17.700 --> 17:19.467 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
SO, WE UNDERSTAND IT IS A

