OBLIGATION TO SAY TO THEM, "HEY,

18:13.200 --> 18:14.600 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
YOU MAY BE IN-NETWORK AT THIS

18:14.600 --> 18:16.133 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
FACILITY, BUT NOT ALL THE

