18:16.800 --> 18:17.967 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
NETWORK."

18:17.967 --> 18:19.433 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
>> IN THE EMERGENCY SITUATION,

18:19.433 --> 18:20.167 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MOST PEOPLE ARE NOT THINKING

18:20.167 --> 18:21.433 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
ABOUT IT.

18:21.433 --> 18:22.733 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
WE'RE NOT GOING TO HAVE ALL OF A

